#~ msgid "Delay between each preload batch. Each batch sends up to 10 URLs in sequence, then waits this many seconds before the next batch via WP-Cron. Higher values reduce server load but take longer to complete. Preloading automatically pauses if server load is too high (exceeds 80% of CPU core count, or load spike detected)."
